@@ -1824,6 +1824,14 @@ changes:
 
 Disable using [syntax detection][] to determine module type.
 
+### `--no-experimental-fetch`
+
+<!-- YAML
+added: v18.0.0
+-->
+
+Disable exposition of Fetch API on the global scope.
+
 ### `--no-experimental-global-navigator`
 
